text: Gabrielle Anne Carteris (born January 2, 1961 in Scottsdale, Arizona ) is an American actress. She has performed on television. She may be best known for playing Andrea Zuckerman on the television series Beverly Hills, 90210. On April 9, 2016, Carteris was elected SAG-AFTRA president. ==References== Category:Actors from Arizona Category:American television actors Category:Presidents of SAG-AFTRA Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:People from Scottsdale, Arizona
